# ForwardSun Technology Project Rules

Production Next.js + TypeScript + Tailwind website for ForwardSun Technology, a solar
energy business focused on Lahore.

## Business Details

- Business name: ForwardSun Technology
- Domain: forwardsuntechnology.com / www.forwardsuntechnology.com
- Location: DHA Rahbar, Lahore
- Service area: Lahore, Pakistan
- Phone / WhatsApp: +92 330 5259922
- Main CTA: "Get Free Assessment"
- Contact form goal: solar assessment leads
- Lead email receiver: hariskhan@forwardsuntechnology.com

## Development Rules

- Do not redesign the website unless explicitly asked.
- Do not change branding, layout direction, colors, or navigation without approval.
- Do not change contact form fields unless explicitly asked.
- Do not change API/email/Resend logic unless the task requires it.
- Always keep the website production-ready.
- Always preserve mobile responsiveness.
- Always use TypeScript-safe code.
- Never hardcode secrets.
- Environment variables must stay in `.env.example` as placeholders only.
- After code changes, run:
  ```
  npm run lint
  npm run typecheck
  npm run build
  ```

## Tracking Rules

- GA4 uses `NEXT_PUBLIC_GA_MEASUREMENT_ID`.
- Do not hardcode the GA4 Measurement ID in code.
- Track lead-generation actions carefully.

## Git Rules

- Make small, focused changes.
- Do not mix unrelated tasks.
- Before commit, explain files changed and why.
